	(text "Rationalle for Connector\n\n3 pin (24V Supply) \n\nPROs:\n\n- More condense\n- Slighitly simpler Layout\n\nCONs:\n\n- No backup line\n- Not as fault tolerant \n\n\n4 pin connector (24 V)\n\nPROs:\n\n- Includes backup signal \n- More proofed\n\nCONs:\n\n- Slightly larger\n"
		(exclude_from_sim no)
