		(uuid "9ab0c620-91d1-4ac5-bff5-4ae9fe06739c")
	)
	(text "Logic (Communication)\n\n- Receives signal from PSOM\n\n- Interprets color and brightness\n\n- Sends data to next LED (chain)\n\n- 5 volt power supply\n\n\n\nFor (WS2814)\n\n- LED has built in IC for the sole\npurpose of processing input signal"
